{"tid":1219642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[夏日必備] 氣壓噴壺","createTime":"2019-06-14T00:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T18:08:29.000Z","uid":51215,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8edc05a380511ee97e001bb49caa490d86597ee3","tid":1219642,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:11:41.000Z","msg":"夏日炎炎 部冷氣用得耐積哂塵 梗係要洗下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我個人比較懶 又唔想整污糟自己隻手喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩既係我係網上面搵到一樣野叫 氣壓噴壺<br />\n相信大家都已經見過架啦 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F43BFT2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF43BFT2.jpg&h=bd64f861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發覺佢十分之好用 將佢較去水柱模式 3米之後都可以噴到個冷氣隔塵網 好使好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0hu0T7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0hu0T7.jpg&h=7f903993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗完冷氣想洗埋車  加D 清潔劑落去 乜都乾淨哂<br />\n記得加左清潔劑唔好噴到人  如果唔係會造成化學燒傷 可大可小架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨左可以拎黎噴野之外 岩岩諗起個噴壺拎去BBQ 用黎救熄個火一流<br />\n噴兩噴乜火都冇哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果覺得唔夠用 可以試埋下面呢兩款 一樣好使好用<br />\n<br />\n介紹返: (圖片有殘體sorry)<br />\n1. 可樂樽氣壓式銅雙頭噴水手持小型噴霧頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dD5TJbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdD5TJbe.jpg&h=9a1030f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztHKPRf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztHKPRf.jpg&h=2799d235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTsVWwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTsVWwf.jpg&h=40b9387d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 伸縮長杆水槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abxbuSp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabxbuSp.jpg&h=f7d2cf9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00gzsD5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00gzsD5.jpg&h=ea7ba33a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 手動氣壓式噴霧器 (加大版)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vgwzsC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvgwzsC9.jpg&h=182fbb2e&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n以下為錯誤示範<br />\n拿拿拿 以下呢D人渣咁樣用氣壓噴壺 同 伸縮長杆水槍 就唔岩啦 加D胡椒水落去噴人傷到人架嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNEtw50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNEtw50.jpg&h=3cc85279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淋花就淋花啦 又要噴鳩人 大家千其千其唔好學呀 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bNJNNE3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbNJNNE3.gif&h=57eaabb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"040abb6eda41f70a51fc5ee096067351de71fcb9","tid":1219642,"uid":51215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e50b29420ddbd81a7c25d738f65962a7dc062f","tid":1219642,"uid":51215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a79157b06441924c97b6183384592db9de0f70","tid":1219642,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:29:52.000Z","msg":"pl"},{"pid":"4a5b92d275608e2f9f691a14c7d32feb0d45e101","tid":1219642,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f1a79157b06441924c97b6183384592db9de0f70","tid":1219642,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:29:52.000Z","msg":"pl"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:30:08.00